Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,/-------------- Part A --------------
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.65,0:01:42.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再过不久 本210航班即将抵达金星
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.35,0:01:47.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金星上用于地球化改造的浮游植物
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.33,0:01:51.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能会令部分乘客产生过敏症状
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.00,0:01:55.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,病症可能会恶化为金星病
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.07,0:02:00.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若出现症状 请立即就医诊疗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.59,0:02:24.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位 安静一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.48,0:02:26.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有人把双手放在脑后
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.55,0:02:28.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要钱我给
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.83,0:02:30.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请放我下去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.35,0:02:32.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敢吵闹的家伙就是这个下场
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.24,0:02:41.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙 为什么偏偏在这个时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.63,0:02:42.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 那边那个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.27,0:02:48.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你听到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.88,0:02:50.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小子 给我醒醒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.65,0:02:52.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.30,0:02:55.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 老老实实把手放到脑后…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.38,0:02:56.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 不准睡 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.82,0:02:58.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道我们是谁吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.20,0:03:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混账
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.01,0:03:15.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.59,0:03:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.77,0:03:21.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此为止的是你们啊 各位赏金头目
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Session #8
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.16,0:03:32.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36\pos(960,980)\fad(1460,0)}Waltz for Venus
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.16,0:03:32.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1460,0)}献给维纳斯的华尔兹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.33,0:03:45.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.97,0:03:47.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一件就要收5000？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.65,0:03:48.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是特殊费用
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.33,0:03:51.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事上面根本没写啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.04,0:03:54.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边不是居住区域啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.06,0:03:57.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你了 能不能通融一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.10,0:04:00.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特地送到那种沙漠里去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.83,0:04:03.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 少敲我竹杠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.15,0:04:04.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.30,0:04:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要送到啊 明白了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.50,0:04:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.26,0:04:19.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.20,0:04:20.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.94,0:04:22.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分钱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.18,0:04:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里分？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.33,0:04:24.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在就要用
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.80,0:04:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那份的钱全在这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.36,0:04:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.93,0:04:37.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又要「存」进赌场了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.52,0:04:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总比存银行好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.92,0:04:42.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不长记性…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.97,0:04:49.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抢匪我还是应付得来的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.44,0:04:56.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厉害…果然厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.68,0:05:03.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是刚才用厉害的招式把劫机犯放倒的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.02,0:05:05.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有事要拜托你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.11,0:05:08.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那招能不能教我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.56,0:05:10.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是柔道 还是功夫？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.29,0:05:16.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.83,0:05:19.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想变得像你那样强
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.82,0:05:22.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这人真烦 说不行就不行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.56,0:05:24.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教我一点点 有什么关系嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.09,0:05:25.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了 师父
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.06,0:05:26.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.58,0:05:30.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.22,0:05:35.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.14,0:05:47.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请等一下 就当救人一命嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.67,0:05:49.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你总归有点同情心的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.52,0:05:50.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在正缺货着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.41,0:05:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你了 对你又没什么损失
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.51,0:06:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么还不快闪…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.99,0:06:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金星上氦气成分很多 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.22,0:06:08.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃了药马上就能治好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.90,0:06:18.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不带这样的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.01,0:06:20.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你自己把药…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.66,0:06:24.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才给你的是润喉糖
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.50,0:06:26.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.66,0:06:28.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔 要实战训练吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.42,0:06:33.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这人啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.08,0:06:35.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫洛可·波纳罗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.66,0:06:37.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多指教了 师父
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.31,0:06:41.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时隔多日的进账
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.75,0:06:43.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会买点好吃的给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.03,0:06:47.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是靠我参谋的本领啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.24,0:06:49.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下个目标是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.00,0:06:58.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫你别用力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.16,0:07:01.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是不那么做的话怎么打倒敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.37,0:07:05.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重要的是顺势借力 而不是靠蛮力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.76,0:07:06.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.64,0:07:08.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要变得像水一般
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.56,0:07:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你懂了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.09,0:07:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不懂…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.89,0:07:14.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想也是 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.48,0:07:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 你用刀刺过来试试
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.53,0:07:19.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会受伤的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.57,0:07:20.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事 照做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.08,0:07:24.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我上了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.88,0:07:33.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.25,0:07:38.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我完全没有用力 只是利用了你的蛮力而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.61,0:07:41.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要掌控力道的流向
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.49,0:07:47.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为此要放松全身的力量以应对敌人所有的动作 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.20,0:07:51.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 变得像流水一般
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.23,0:07:52.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.74,0:07:56.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 水可以化为任何形状
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.45,0:08:00.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既能平缓流动 也能澎湃喷薄 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.44,0:08:06.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉有些似懂非懂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.70,0:08:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对老年人放尊重点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.16,0:08:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这东西拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.54,0:08:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚…不 明天晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.19,0:08:19.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在城郊的教堂碰头
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.65,0:08:20.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.76,0:08:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里！ 别让他逃了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.96,0:08:29.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去赌场了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.93,0:08:32.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里的赌场可是以吝啬闻名的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.77,0:08:34.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不用在意 反正是她的钱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.46,0:08:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还是个一去不回的家伙 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.37,0:08:39.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道她啥时候回来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.05,0:08:45.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干等着太浪费 不如赚点零花钱打发时间吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.60,0:08:50.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮卡罗·加尔文 虽然只是个不值钱的小毛贼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.61,0:08:53.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这次豁出去干了票大的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.46,0:08:57.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是把这伙人抓住 赏金翻倍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.79,0:09:01.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被偷的是这玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.81,0:09:03.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是治疗金星病的特效药
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.83,0:09:07.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由于难以栽培 似乎价值几千万
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.23,0:09:22.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 跑哪儿去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.17,0:09:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畜生 逃得倒是挺快
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.21,0:09:37.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己吞了不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.60,0:09:40.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起抓那伙人更值钱不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.21,0:09:43.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.51,0:09:45.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你刚才犹豫了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.33,0:09:49.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 这种危险的东西就该不碰才对
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.06,0:09:50.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要不败露就好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.46,0:09:53.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在赌场输了多少
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.86,0:09:54.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问这干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.54,0:09:56.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮卡罗交给你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.09,0:09:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去追洛可
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.82,0:10:00.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等着不就行了 反正说好碰头的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.99,0:10:04.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俗话说「赏金女神是转瞬即逝的」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.50,0:10:07.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是幸运女神吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.12,0:10:15.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿梭机的残骸？怎么会在那种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.46,0:10:16.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.65,0:10:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说或许是有些爱折腾的人会特意住在沙漠里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.83,0:10:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过话说回来…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.31,0:11:18.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许动
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,/-------------- Part B --------------
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.19,0:11:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许动 举起双手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.59,0:11:35.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是可疑人物…说这话反而更可疑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.39,0:11:38.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁 为什么来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.29,0:11:42.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.81,0:11:46.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.70,0:11:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是来找洛可的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.94,0:11:54.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是洛可的朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.45,0:11:55.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？啊…不
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.16,0:11:57.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.13,0:12:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 洗手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.96,0:12:14.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,BOSS 还是找不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.73,0:12:17.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.74,0:12:21.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 飘浮在空中的植物 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.65,0:12:22.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为那个的缘故
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.33,0:12:26.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它偶尔会降下像雪一般的孢子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.43,0:12:29.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对一般人好像没影响 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.11,0:12:32.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我由于体质原因而失明了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.92,0:12:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没觉得不方便吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.27,0:12:36.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有 习惯了就无所谓了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.55,0:12:41.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 有些事情盲人反而更明白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.17,0:12:43.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能治好吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.46,0:12:45.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯花钱就行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.96,0:12:51.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是觉得这样也无妨 但是洛可他…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.39,0:12:53.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他很疼妹妹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.39,0:12:58.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是昨天洛可送来的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.03,0:13:09.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然大家都说洛可不好 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.55,0:13:15.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的确有些坏朋友…但洛可是好人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.59,0:13:19.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定我也是这些坏朋友之一哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.78,0:13:23.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 或许吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.60,0:13:25.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 你不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.93,0:13:28.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.70,0:13:31.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛可和你 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.59,0:13:34.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然别人很难明白 但你们都拥有美丽的心灵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.48,0:13:38.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因为我明白这点 所以才会请你喝茶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.40,0:13:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美丽的心灵吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.72,0:13:57.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许那东西很久以前…就已失去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.08,0:14:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要找皮卡罗 告诉我他在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.69,0:14:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 我可不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.66,0:14:31.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能想得起来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.66,0:14:34.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.29,0:14:38.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 Grey Ash种子的价格？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.06,0:14:40.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是问一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.42,0:14:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别傻了 那东西简直堪比宝石
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.56,0:14:45.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是有幸看到就够好运了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.15,0:14:51.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真要卖的话估计很困难
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.29,0:14:54.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过一颗估计能值八百万左右…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.53,0:14:56.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你拿到了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.86,0:14:57.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.77,0:14:58.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.63,0:15:00.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮卡罗那边呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.60,0:15:04.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还差点儿 你那边也加油干啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.41,0:15:18.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 洛可 你最好乖乖告诉我们把那盆东西藏哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.91,0:15:20.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不说的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.80,0:15:23.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思啊 我弄丢了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.51,0:15:25.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说不管用吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.49,0:15:39.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛可啊 听说你有个妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.43,0:15:40.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这事和我妹妹无关
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.29,0:15:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼哼 那究竟在哪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.31,0:15:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这 这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.92,0:15:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想见皮卡罗 告诉我他在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.25,0:16:03.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 他在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.81,0:16:34.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.13,0:16:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.85,0:16:39.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完整无缺地帮你带来了哦 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.86,0:16:42.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 里面的东西我看过了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.84,0:16:45.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道那是什么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.42,0:16:47.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Grey Ash
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.75,0:16:49.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字挺普通的 不过倒是个厉害玩意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.06,0:16:53.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为值你们十倍的赏金啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.26,0:16:58.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…是赏金猎人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.66,0:17:01.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为了抓我而来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.73,0:17:06.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯黛拉需要这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.99,0:17:14.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃 你会被杀的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.36,0:17:19.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 这不只是像傻瓜一样兜了个大圈子嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.88,0:17:21.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰特 听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.52,0:17:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住 住手吧 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.99,0:17:34.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Grey Ash还给你们 这样总行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.02,0:17:37.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放他走吧 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.09,0:17:42.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思让你特地送来啊 谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.49,0:17:46.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这小子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.89,0:17:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点干掉他们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.21,0:18:04.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮卡罗·加尔文 乖乖投降吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.25,0:18:13.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不能干得优雅点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.48,0:18:20.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 别杀掉啊 想让赏金泡汤吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.56,0:18:22.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘁 赏金猎人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.85,0:18:24.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上把货抢回来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.65,0:18:28.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛可！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.12,0:18:50.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛可！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.51,0:19:00.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 一群蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.14,0:19:04.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 让人费了那么多工夫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.98,0:19:07.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.48,0:19:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还活着吗 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.48,0:19:15.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,师父 看到刚才那招了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.93,0:19:19.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 别说话 我马上叫医生来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.18,0:19:20.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.83,0:19:26.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 把八音盒…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.74,0:19:29.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 斯黛拉的事包在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.91,0:19:31.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.40,0:19:32.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 等一下 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.37,0:19:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听着 别死 别死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.13,0:19:47.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是能早点认识你的话…我们会…成为朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.50,0:20:11.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请进
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.28,0:20:15.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛可 是洛可吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.13,0:20:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他的代理
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.68,0:20:20.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你也好 听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.93,0:20:24.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛可拿到了Grey Ash 手术费也有了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.83,0:20:26.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的眼睛可以治好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.90,0:20:28.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害啊 怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.63,0:20:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我第一眼想看到洛可
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.35,0:20:33.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以请帮我转达 让他马上来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.34,0:20:34.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之越快越好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.35,0:20:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道他被抓了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.00,0:20:41.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.49,0:20:44.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么为什么不来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.73,0:20:55.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他死了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.49,0:21:00.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.53,0:21:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯黛拉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.14,0:21:05.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事 请回吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.55,0:21:10.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的 洛可是因为做了坏事才死的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.84,0:21:14.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你 今天就回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.04,0:21:27.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…从没有用这双眼睛看过洛可的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.61,0:21:32.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 真正的洛可是个怎样的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.34,0:21:34.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算看不见也能明白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.20,0:21:36.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是个好人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.93,0:21:38.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像你知道的那样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.71,0:21:45.71,IN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnFZLanTingHei-R-GBK\fs36\fad(300,300)\an9}BGM：「Memory」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,/-------------- ED：「The Real Folk Blues」--------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.42,0:22:45.69,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}愛してたと嘆くには
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.09,0:22:50.78,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}あまりにも時は過ぎてしまった
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.38,0:22:57.37,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}まだ心のほころびを
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.09,0:23:02.78,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}癒せぬまま　風が吹いてる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.38,0:23:12.62,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}乾いた瞳で誰か泣いてくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.45,0:23:18.74,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}THE REAL FOLK BLUES
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.89,0:23:27.13,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}本当の悲しみが知りたいだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.45,0:23:39.32,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}泥の河に浸かった人生も悪くはない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.65,0:23:47.69,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}一度きりで終わるなら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.42,0:22:45.69,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\an8}想要感慨曾经爱过
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.09,0:22:50.78,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\an8}岁月却已逝去许久
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.38,0:22:57.37,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\an8}心头伤痕尚未愈合
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.09,0:23:02.78,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\an8}风儿却已经吹起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.38,0:23:12.62,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\an8}谁会用干涸的眼眸为我落泪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.89,0:23:27.13,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\an8}但求知晓真正的伤悲
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.45,0:23:39.32,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\an8}置身泥沼的人生倒也不坏
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.65,0:23:47.69,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\an8}只要此生何需来世
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,/-------------- Next --------------
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.14,0:24:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从下周起 爱德要出场啦 嘿嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.46,0:24:12.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿什么嘿 你谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.79,0:24:14.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 来自我介绍
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.76,0:24:18.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱德华·王·侯·皮皮鲁·提布鲁斯基四世哟
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.51,0:24:19.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这名字真够长的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.93,0:24:20.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.99,0:24:24.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字是我自己取的 很酷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.20,0:24:25.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四世是什么意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.14,0:24:26.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.90,0:24:28.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36\pos(960,980)}Jamming with Edward
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.90,0:24:28.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与艾德华竞飙
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.69,0:24:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说这孩子是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.76,0:24:32.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要看哦




